  - Title: Chârtdogya Upanishad
    Book:
      - VI
      - Chapter:
          - ii
          - Verse: 2-3
Tags:
  - Creation=Creation by Pairs
  - Creation=Self-Revelation
---
In the beginning this world was just Being, one only, without a second. It
bethought itself： ‘Would that I were many! Let me procreate myself!’
